<activity xml:id="act-contemosOrganicemosContemos" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Contemos, reorganicemos, contemos</title>

<statement>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-141776">
    <shortdescription>tablero de 5</shortdescription>
  </image>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students count and rearrange the connecting cubes. Students may count the connecting cubes again or know that the quantity is the same without recounting.</p>
  </solution>


