  <!-- Síntesis de la actividad -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Display 6 connecting cubes.</li>
      <li>
        <q>¿Cómo puedo saber cuántos cubos encajables hay?</q> (You can count them. You can put them in a line and count them.)
      </li>
      <li>Demonstrate or invite a student to demonstrate counting the connecting cubes.</li>
      <li>
        <q>Cuéntenle a su compañero cuántos cubos encajables hay</q> (There are 6 connecting cubes.)
      </li>
      <li>Rearrange the connecting cubes on the 5-frame, putting each cube in a square and one cube under the 5-frame, as pictured:</li>
    </ul>
    <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-141777">
      <shortdescription>cubos encajables y tablero de 5</shortdescription>
    </image>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <q>¿Cómo puedo saber cuántos cubos encajables hay?</q> (There are still 6, you just moved them around. You can count them.)
      </li>
      <li>Invite a student to explain how they know that there are still 6 connecting cubes without counting them again.</li>
      <li>If needed, invite a student to count the connecting cubes.</li>
      <li>
        <q>Todavía hay 6 cubos encajables. Los movimos, pero aún hay el mismo número de cubos encajables</q>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


